《'''76天'''》（{{lang-en|''76 Days''}}）是2020年美国纪录片，由[[吴皓_(导演)|吴皓]]、陈玮曦和佚名执导，于[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]爆发初期拍摄。影片捕捉了[[武汉市|武汉市]]因[[2019冠状病毒病武汉市疫情|疫情]][[2019冠状病毒病中国大陆疫区封锁措施|封城]]期间的社会百态<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2020/09/76-days-documentary-wuhan-lockdown-coronavirus/616450/|title='76 Days' Is Unwatchable Yet Utterly Compelling|first=David|last=Sims|date=2020-09-24|website=The Atlantic|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111081017/https://www.theatlantic.com/culture/archive/2020/09/76-days-documentary-wuhan-lockdown-coronavirus/616450/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/22/movies/toronto-international-film-festival.html|title=We Watched Fall Film Festivals From Home. Here's How It Went.|first1=Manohla|last1=Dargis|first2=A. O.|last2=Scott|date=2020-09-22|via=NYTimes.com|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114093632/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/09/22/movies/toronto-international-film-festival.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片于2020年9月14日在[[多伦多国际电影节|多伦多国际电影节]]全球首映，收获好评<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=76 Days|url=https://www.tiff.net/events/76-days|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129122831/https://www.tiff.net/events/76-days|archive-date=2020-11-29|access-date=2020-09-24|website=TIFF|language=en}}</ref>。之后由{{tsl|en|MTV Films|MTV电影|MTV纪录片}}于2020年12月4日在美国发行。

== 制作 ==
2020年2月，武汉刚封城，影片的拍摄工作就在武汉的四家医院[[武汉协和医院|武汉协和医院]]、[[武汉同济医院|武汉同济医院]]、[[武汉红十字会医院|武汉红十字会医院]]和[[武汉市儿童医院|武汉市儿童医院]]进行<ref>{{Cite web|last1=Toronto|first1=Point of View Magazine • 392-401 Richmond Street West •|last2=email|first2=ON • M5V 3A8 • Canada •639-0653 • Send us an|title=TIFF Talk: Hao Wu Takes Audiences to the Frontlines of Wuhan in COVID Doc 76 Days – Point of View Magazine|url=http://povmagazine.com/articles/view/tiff-talk-hao-wu-takes-audiences-to-the-frontlines-of-wuhan-in-covid-doc-76|access-date=2020-09-24|website=povmagazine.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206152857/http://povmagazine.com/articles/view/tiff-talk-hao-wu-takes-audiences-to-the-frontlines-of-wuhan-in-covid-doc-76|dead-url=no}}</ref>。封城期间，各医院只允许病人、医护人员和记者进入，少数几家医院只批准官方严格批准的记者和摄影团队进入<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Qin|first1=Amy|last2=Wee|first2=Sui-Lee|date=2020-03-06|title='No Way Out': In China, Coronavirus Takes Toll on Other Patients|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/03/world/asia/china-coronavirus-cancer.html|access-date=2020-09-24|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221223639/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/03/world/asia/china-coronavirus-cancer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，并非所有医院在封城由始至终都采取严格的管控措施，最开始形势严峻混乱的时候，医疗物资严重短缺，许多医院实际上欢迎媒体采访，以此寻求帮助。中国其他地方的部分医疗团队驰援武汉的过程也开放拍摄，一部分原因，是他们希望自己在这一历史性时刻的影响能够留存下来。

2月中旬，吴皓正计划为美国一家电视台拍摄关于疫情的纪录片，于是找来两位合作导演<ref>{{Cite web|last=Gui|first=de Mulder|date=|title=76 DAYS (2020) - Hao Wu Exclusive Interview|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qa9Xi7BM_d8|dead-url=no|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=|website=}}</ref>。三人于2月初便开始在武汉城内进行拍摄。他们会在线上分享原片，商讨拍摄策略。然而到了3月底，由于地缘政治上的紧张局势日益加剧，中国大幅度收紧媒体对疫情的报道，因此两名导演决定暂停和吴皓合作。吴皓利用在亚特兰大接受隔离检疫及电视台取消这个项目的时候，剪辑另外两位导演的片段。完成粗剪后，他立马联系了两位导演，两人最终同意和他完成影片。

和片中的医护人员一样，陈玮曦和吴皓每天都要穿着全套防护装备，这套衣服穿起来很不舒服，会阻碍呼吸，他们有好几次都觉得不舒服。一旦进入污染区，他们就要一次待四个小时，不能休息上厕所，和医生护士一样。每天晚上结束拍摄，他们都要全身消毒，才回到为前线人员安排的酒店单独休息。拍摄团队在封城期间都是身心交瘁的<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|last=AsiaNews.it|title='76 days', a film about horror and heroism in Wuhan|url=http://www.asianews.it/news-en/%2776-days%27%2C-a-film-about-horror-and-heroism-in-Wuhan-51078.html|access-date=2020-09-24|website=www.asianews.it|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026012851/http://www.asianews.it/news-en/%2776-days%27%2C-a-film-about-horror-and-heroism-in-Wuhan-51078.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

随着社会秩序的逐渐恢复，武汉最终于4月8日正式解封。

==发行==
影片于2020年9月14日在[[多伦多国际电影节|多伦多国际电影节]]首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tiff.net/events/76-days|title=76 Days|website=Toronto International Film Festival|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129122831/https://www.tiff.net/events/76-days|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不久后，{{tsl|en|MTV Films|MTV电影|MTV纪录片}}买下影片美国发行权<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/wuhan-china-documentary-mtv-documentary-films-toronto-festival-docu-76-days-1234596437/|title=MTV Documentary Films Acquires Toronto Docu ’76 Days’ On COVID Outbreak In Wuhan, China|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101032926/https://deadline.com/2020/10/wuhan-china-documentary-mtv-documentary-films-toronto-festival-docu-76-days-1234596437/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年10月16日，影片在[[美国电影学会|美国电影学会]]试映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/afi-fest-2020-full-lineup-1234590916/|title=AFI FEST 2020 Announces Full Lineup, Including Majority Female-Directed Films|website=IndieWire|first=Kate|last=Erbland|date=2020-10-06|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020004611/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/10/afi-fest-2020-full-lineup-1234590916/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://fest.afi.com/2020/documentary-2020/76-days#elevent|title=76 Days|website=AFI Fest|accessdate=2020-10-16|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026063607/https://fest.afi.com/2020/documentary-2020/76-days/#elevent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月4日，影片在美国上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/11/76-days-release-date-mtv-documentary-films-hao-wu-weixi-chen-1234608110/|title=’76 Days’: MTV Documentary Films Sets Release Date For COVID-19 Docu|date=2020-11-02|author=Dino-Ray Ramos|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2020-11-02|archive-date=2020-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201207005432/https://deadline.com/2020/11/76-days-release-date-mtv-documentary-films-hao-wu-weixi-chen-1234608110/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]根据73条评论打出100%的新鲜度，平均得分8.0/10。网站共识写道：“《76天》原始、纪实性地回顾2019冠状病毒病疫情初期武汉市医院的日常，是一部引人入胜、强有力的纪录片，是一副令人出奇地感到舒适的肖像画”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/76_days|title=76 Days (2020)|work=Rotten Tomatoes|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123165215/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/76_days|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论19条，平均得分85/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/76-days|title=76 Days|work=Metacritic|access-date=2021-01-01|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206175237/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/76-days|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

